OL,7,FCadbury's first shop has been
OL,8,Frecreated using more than 600 bars of
OL,9,FDairy Milk to mark the company's 200th
OL,10,Fanniversary.
OL,12,FIn 1824, John Cadbury opened the first
OL,13,FCadbury shop at in Birmingham,
OL,14,Fcomplete with plate glass windows with
OL,15,Fmahogany frames, which he was said to
OL,16,Fhave cleaned every day.
