OL,7,FThis feature and a front door similar
OL,8,Fto the original have been replicated
OL,9,Fby chocolatiers Donna Oluban and Dawn
OL,10,FJenks from Cadbury World in
OL,11,FBournville, Birmingham.
OL,13,FThey took five days to craft every
OL,14,Felement of the creation, which is 85cm
OL,15,Ftall and weighs 30kg ` the equivalent
OL,16,Fof 667 standard Cadbury Dairy Milk
OL,17,Fbars.
