OL,7,FColin Pitt, education and heritage
OL,8,Fcentre manager at Cadbury World, said:
OL,9,F"We are always so impressed by the
OL,10,Fstunning creations our chocolatiers
OL,11,Fcreate here at Cadbury World, and with
OL,12,Fsuch an important milestone year for
OL,13,Fthe brand, this one had to be extra
OL,14,Fspecial.
