OL,7,F"We're proud of the Cadbury story and
OL,8,Fguests of all ages really enjoy
OL,9,Flearning the heritage of the brand
OL,10,Fhere at the attraction, so what better
OL,11,Fway to honour the 200 years of Cadbury
OL,12,Fthan with a throwback to where it all
OL,13,Fbegan, the Bull Street shop."
OL,15,FThe creation will be on display to
OL,16,Fcoincide with the reopening of the
OL,17,Fimproved Bournville Experience.
